# **PHASE 1 — Base System Setup & Lightweight Architecture**

* Create Django project with modular app structure
* Configure MySQL + optimized connection pooling
* Add Bootstrap CDN + custom gradient theme
* Install minimal reusable components
* Implement simple layout template with soft shadows + rounded corners

---

# **PHASE 2 — Ultra-Simple Auth & Role Access**

* Add Login/Logout with clean, mobile-first UI
* Create roles: **Admin, Manager, Cashier**
* Add role-based page permissions
* Create easy switch-panel for Admin/Manager navigation

---

# **PHASE 3 — Smart System Settings (Central Control Page)**

* Add "System Settings" page (business name, currency, logo)
* Toggle options: show/hide inventory, receipts, analytics
* Theme customizer (color gradients, shadows, card styles)
* Store branding for receipts & dashboard

---

# **PHASE 4 — Smart Field & Category Builder (Simplified Version)**

* Admin creates **Categories** like “Product Info”, “Payment Info”, “Customer Info”
* Admin adds **Fields** (text, number, dropdown) with fewer options
* Switches: *required*, *show on receipt*, *show on reports*
* Auto-generate forms based only on what admin needs (no overload)

---

# **PHASE 5 — Dynamic Form Engine (Cleaner & Faster)**

* Read admin-created fields
* Render POS input form automatically
* Simple validation rules
* Store dynamic field entries cleanly in a unified structure

